sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant R as BTH Reserve
    participant W as BTH Watcher (SCP)
    participant F as Federation (t-of-n)
    participant D as Destination contract<br/>(Ethereum / Solana)

    U->>R: Lock deposit (factor-1 BTH)
    alt factor-1 deposit
        R->>W: Await SCP finality
        W->>F: Confirmed final deposit
        F->>F: Collect t-of-n attestation<br/>(domain-separated, order-bound)
        F->>D: bridgeMint(to, amount, orderId)
        D-->>U: wBTH minted (exactly-once / orderId)
    else non-factor-1 deposit
        R-->>U: Rejected before any mint<br/>(audit event, never mints)
    end
